                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="far fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text mb-0">
                    I was a bit nervous to be buying a secondhand phone from Amazon, but I couldn't be happier with my purchase!! I have a pre-paid data plan so I was worried that this phone wouldn't connect with my data plan, since the new phones don't have the physical Sim tray anymore, but couldn't have been easier! I bought an Unlocked black iPhone 14 Pro Max in excellent condition and everything is PERFECT. It was super easy to set up and the phone works and looks great. It truly was in excellent condition. Highly recommend!!!<i class="fas fa-heart text-dark ms-1"></i>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Review 2 -->
        <div class="review-item d-flex gap-3">
            <div class="avatar-container flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Ronald Richards" class="rounded-circle avatar-img">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow-1">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1">
                    <h6 class="reviewer-name mb-0">Ronald Richards</h6>
                    <span class="review-date">24 January,2023</span>
                </div>
                <div class="star-color small mb-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text mb-0">
                    This phone has 1T storage and is durable. Plus all the new iPhones have a C port! Apple is phasing out the current ones! (All about the Benjamin's) So if you want a phone that's going to last grab an iPhone 14 pro max and get several cords and plugs.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Review 3 -->
        <div class="review-item d-flex gap-3">
            <div class="avatar-container flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg" alt="Darcy King" class="rounded-circle avatar-img">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow-1">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1">
                    <h6 class="reviewer-name mb-0">Darcy King</h6>
                    <span class="review-date">24 January,2023</span>
                </div>
                <div class="star-color small mb-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="far fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="review-text mb-3">
                    I might be the only one to say this but the camera is a little funky. Hoping it will change with a software update: otherwise, love this phone! Came in great condition
                </p>
                <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                    <!-- Placeholder images for attached review photos -->
                    @* <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592750475338-74b7b21085ab?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&q=80" alt="Phone back" class="review-attached-img">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605236453806-6ff36851218e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=150&q=80" alt="Phone side" class="review-attached-img"> *@
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- View More Button -->
    <div class="text-center mt-3">
        <button class="btn btn-view-more">
            View More <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ms-1 small"></i>
        </button>
    </div>

</div>

<!-- Bootstrap 5 JS Bundle (Includes Popper) -->






    <div class="m-3 ">
    <h5 class="display-5 text-center mb-4">  Related Products </h5>
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-evenly ">
    @foreach(var suggetions in Model.SuggestedProducts)
    {



            <!-- Product Card HTML -->
            <div class="product-card m-2 col-3" style="background-color:">
                <!-- Wishlist Icon -->
                @* <div class="wishlist-btn">
                            <i class="bi bi-heart"></i>
                        </div> *@

                <!-- Image -->
                <div class="product-img-container">
                    <img src="@suggetions.ImageUrl" alt="@suggetions.Title">
                </div>

                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h5 class="product-title">
                        @suggetions.Title
                    </h5>

                    <div class="price-tag">@suggetions.Price</div>
                    <form method="get">
                        <button class="btn-buy  buyBtn  " asp-controller="Product"
                                asp-action="Details"
                                asp-route-id="@suggetions.Id" id="@suggetions.Id">
                            Buy Now
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>




    }
    </div>
</div>


 @section Scripts {
    <script>

        
        $(document).ready(function () {

                    $('.goto').click(function () {
                         var btn = $(this)
                    var id = btn.attr("id")

                    window.location.href = `/Product/Details/${id}`;
                    })
                    $('.goto2').click(function () {
                         var btn = $(this)
                    var id = btn.attr("id")
                    alert("goto")
                    window.location.href = `/Cart`;
                    })

            var quatity = 1;
                    $('#Add').click(function () {

                        var quatityDiv = $(".Quatity");
                        if(quatity < 5){
                            quatity++;
                            quatityDiv.html(quatity)

                        }

                    })
                    $('#Minus').click(function () {
                          var quatityDiv = $(".Quatity");
                        if(quatity  > 0){
                            quatity--;
                            quatityDiv.html(quatity)

                        }

                    })
                $('.BuyNow').click(function () {
                    var btn = $(this)
                    var id = btn.attr("id")
                    console.log(id)
                    var quatityDiv = $(".Quatity");
                    if(quatity == 0){
                    quatity++

                    }
                    quatityDiv.html(quatity)

                    if(quatity != 0){
                        var count = quatity
                    }

                    var isBuyNow = btn.data("buynow");
                    if(!isBuyNow){
                        quatity = 1
                        quatityDiv.html("✅")
                    }
                   $.ajax({
                        url: `/Cart/AddToCart/${id}`,
                        type: 'Post',                        
                        data: {
                            id: id,
                            quatity:count

                        },
                        success: function (response) {
                            
                            // alert("Success: " + response.message);
                            console.log(response);
                            if(isBuyNow){
                                window.location.href = '/Cart/Index';
                                quatity = 1
                    }else{

                    // window.location.reload()
                    }
                        },
                        error: function (xhr, status, error) {
                            
                            console.error("Error occurred: " + error);
                        }
                    });
                
               
            });
        });


                function changeImage(element, imageUrl) {
            // 1. Change the main image source
            const mainImage = document.getElementById('mainImage');

            // Simple fade effect
            mainImage.style.opacity = '0';

            setTimeout(() => {
                mainImage.src = imageUrl;
                mainImage.style.opacity = '1';
            }, 150);

            // 2. Update active thumbnail styling
            const thumbnails = document.querySelectorAll('.thumb-item');
            thumbnails.forEach(thumb => thumb.classList.remove('active'));
            element.classList.add('active');
        }
           const toastTrigger = document.querySelector('.addToCartBtn');
        const toastLiveExample = document.getElementById('cartToast');

        if (toastTrigger) {
          const toastBootstrap = bootstrap.Toast.getOrCreateInstance(toastLiveExample);
          toastTrigger.addEventListener('click', () => {
            toastBootstrap.show(); // Displays the toast
          });
        }

    </script>
} 